Class AuditEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.auditservice.transport.AuditEntry

  • public class AuditEntry
extends Object
    A piece of audit information that references the affected Item and the Principal who triggered the change.
    Since:
    2.0
